          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/242268.Desert_Solitaire">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/248667-christy?shelf=memoir-and-autobiography">memoir-and-autobiography</a>, 
